            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title"><small class="text-muted fw-light">Core identity</small></h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li>Web app <==> web api</li>
              <li>JWT token authentication</li>
              <li>MVC cookie auth using issued JWT token</li>
              <li>Customized user identity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm border-primary">
          <div class="card-header py-3 text-white bg-primary border-primary">
            <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Technology stack</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title"><small class="text-muted fw-light">.Net core mvc / web api</small></h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li>C#</li>
              <li>MVC / Razor</li>
              <li>Bootstrap / JQuery / Javascript</li>
              <li>Code first / SQL Server</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm border-primary">
          <div class="card-header py-3 text-white bg-primary border-primary">
            <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Design</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title"><small class="text-muted fw-light">Domain driven design</small></h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li>Clean architecture</li>
              <li>Entity framework</li>
              <li>CQRS / repository /mediarR</li>
              <li>Responsive ui / Fluent validation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm border-primary">
          <div class="card-header py-3 text-white bg-primary border-primary">
            <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Security</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title"><small class="text-muted fw-light">OWASP</small></h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li></li>
              <li>CSP middleware - add csp header /report csp failures</li>
              <li>Security headers middleware auto add </li>
