            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title"><small class="text-muted fw-light">Azure</small></h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li></li>
              <li>Sites hosted in azure app service</li>
              <li>Azure blob/cdn storage for file upload</li>
              <li>Azure sql server database</li>
              <li>Automated builds git hub actions</li>
              <li>Automated deployments git hub actions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
